<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Donation Reminder</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Donation Reminder</h1>
  <p>Dear <%= @donor.name %>,</p>
  <p>This is a friendly reminder that your scheduled donation to support the charity "<%= @charity.name %>" is coming up soon. The donation date is <%= @donation_date %>.</p>
  <p>Thank you for your continued support!</p>
  <p>Best regards,</p>
  <p>The Donation Platform Team</p>
</body>
</html>
